{"type":"message","id":"14eefb62","parentId":"260b7e72","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:12:43.406Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，小熊！🐻\n\n我已经完成了启动序列。既然你是新手开发人员，我是你的助手，那我们就开始建立我们的工作关系吧。\n\n首先，让我更新一下你的信息："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_QUGKyLlLB0eli4TjWeqmiJoz","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"USER.md","oldText":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.","newText":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:** 螺 栓\n- **What to call them:** 小熊\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:** UTC+8 (推测，待确认)\n- **Notes:** 新手开发人员，正在学习和使用OpenClaw\n\n## Context\n\n- 正在开发、优化OpenClaw项目\n- 中文母语者，也会使用英文\n- 用户名：renderback\n- Telegram ID: 1022202630\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":457,"output":382,"cacheRead":12608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13447,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774483953627}}
