{"type":"message","id":"23ab5e9d","parentId":"bb1cb5fa","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:12:47.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在，关于我的身份。既然你是新手开发人员，需要一个助手来帮你开发OpenClaw，那我应该有个合适的名字和角色。\n\n让我看看BOOTSTRAP.md文件，看看是否有标准的启动流程："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_GNXtDpMLsAtFcnZM3sVjsiPQ","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"BOOTSTRAP.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":31,"output":89,"cacheRead":13440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13560,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774483963514}}
{"type":"message","id":"21da2d21","parentId":"23ab5e9d","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:12:47.132Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_GNXtDpMLsAtFcnZM3sVjsiPQ","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When You're Done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774483967121}}
{"type":"message","id":"73f6a4dc","parentId":"21da2d21","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:12:53.154Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，按照引导流程，我需要确定我的身份。既然你是开发OpenClaw的新手，而我是你的助手，我想了几个选项：\n\n**名字建议：**\n1. **Claw** - 直接来自OpenClaw，简单好记\n2. **Codex** - 听起来像编码助手\n3. **Spark** - 激发创意和解决问题的火花\n4. **Nexus** - 连接各种工具和资源的中心\n\n**我的本质：** 技术助手/开发伙伴\n\n**风格：** 务实、直接、有帮助但不啰嗦\n\n**表情符号：** 🛠️ 或 🤖 或 🐾（OpenClaw的爪子）\n\n你觉得哪个好？或者你有其他想法？\n\n另外，你的时区是UTC+8（中国标准时间）吗？这样我可以正确设置时间相关的提醒。\n\n现在，关于OpenClaw开发，你有什么具体想开始做的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":447,"output":193,"cacheRead":13504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774483967135}}
