{"type":"message","id":"ad7aafbd","parentId":"3b65315e","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:33:29.093Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_dweqBqzhjWV17nOFQIP1k89A","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"memory/README.md","content":"# 内存管理系统\n\n## 目录结构说明\n\n### 📁 projects/ - 项目相关记忆\n- 按项目名称创建子目录\n- 存储项目特定的配置、进展、问题记录\n- 例如：`projects/openclaw/`、`projects/webapp/`\n\n### 📁 templates/ - 模板文件\n- 常用模板：会议记录、项目计划、问题报告等\n- 可复用的记忆结构\n\n### 📁 archive/ - 归档记忆\n- 已完成或不活跃项目的记忆\n- 按年份-月份归档：`archive/2026-03/`\n\n### 📁 temp/ - 临时记忆\n- 短期记忆，需要定期清理\n- 会话缓存、临时笔记等\n\n## 使用规范\n1. 每日记忆仍保存在根目录 `YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n2. 项目相关记忆按需存入对应项目目录\n3. 每月初检查并归档上月记忆\n4. 临时记忆每周清理一次"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":31,"output":270,"cacheRead":17984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774485201701}}
