{"type":"message","id":"9806fcf9","parentId":"dd7c2fef","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:33:37.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_WCm6weB3RzyiE0NOwrqDA1DR","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"memory/projects/openclaw.md","content":"# OpenClaw 项目记忆\n\n## 项目信息\n- **负责人**: 熊哥\n- **助手**: 小龙虾🦞\n- **开始日期**: 2026-03-26\n- **状态**: 进行中\n\n## 当前任务\n1. ✅ 系统状态检查 (2026-03-26)\n2. ✅ 身份和目录结构建立 (2026-03-26)\n3. 🔄 配置优化和自动化\n\n## 配置记录\n### 已完成的配置\n- 身份文件：IDENTITY.md\n- 用户信息：USER.md\n- 内存目录结构\n\n### 待完成的配置\n- 定期健康检查\n- 备份策略\n- 日志管理\n\n## 技术栈\n- OpenClaw 2026.3.13\n- Node.js v22.22.1\n- Telegram 集成\n- DeepSeek Chat API\n\n## 遇到的问题\n_(记录开发过程中遇到的问题和解决方案)_\n\n## 学习笔记\n_(记录关于OpenClaw的学习心得和技巧)_"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":73,"output":286,"cacheRead":18240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18599,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774485209177}}
