6-03-26 01:12 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"螺 栓 (1022202630)\",\n  \"id\": \"1022202630\",\n  \"name\": \"螺 栓\",\n  \"username\": \"renderback\"\n}\n```\n\n在吗\n- Assistant: 在的，熊哥！🦞 有什么需要帮忙的吗？\n[non-text content: thinking]\n\n<read-files>\n/home/openclaw/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nSOUL.md\nUSER.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/home/openclaw/.openclaw/log-rotation/config.json\n/home/openclaw/.openclaw/log-rotation/logrotate.sh\n/home/openclaw/.openclaw/log-rotation/restore.sh\n/home/openclaw/.openclaw/log-rotation/test.sh\nMEMORY.md\nmemory/2026-03-26.md\n</modified-files>\n\n<workspace-critical-rules>\n## Session Startup\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Red Lines\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n\n## Decisions\n- 将 TIMESTAMP 格式从 `%Y%m%d_%H%M%S` 改为 `%y%m%d%H%M%S`（缩短年份和去掉分隔符）以解决文件名过长问题\n- 将 rsync 命令改为 cp 命令以解决 `rsync: command not found` 问题\n\n## Open TODOs\n- 修复 \"File name too long\" 错误（问题仍未解决，备份脚本运行后仍报错）\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- 使用 bash 脚本，需要兼容 set -e\n- 备份脚本路径：`/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/backups/backup-script.sh`\n\n## Pending user ask\n- 用户要求排查两个问题：\n  1. `rsync: command not found` 警告 → 已修复（改为cp）\n  2. \"File name too long\" 错误 → **尚未完全修复**\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- 备份脚本路径：`/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/backups/backup-script.sh`\n- 备份输出：`/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/backups/daily/backup_daily_260326022431.tar.gz`\n- 错误信息：`'/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/backups/daily/backup_daily_260326022431.tar.gz': File nam