{"type":"message","id":"c084f36a","parentId":"e9f99b2b","timestamp":"2026-03-26T02:56:40.267Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll create each skill with SKILL.md and optional scripts.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d28122423ab8453be6a1fb9168f94","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: git-manager\ndescription: Git操作自动化 - 提交、推送、查看状态、创建分支。触发词：git提交、git推送、git状态、创建分支、提交代码\n---\n\n# Git Manager\n\n帮助管理Git仓库的常用操作。\n\n## 常用命令\n\n### 查看状态\n```bash\ngit status\ngit status -s\ngit diff\n```\n\n### 提交更改\n```bash\ngit add -A\ngit commit -m \"提交信息\"\n```\n\n### 推送\n```bash\ngit push\ngit push origin <分支名>\n```\n\n### 分支操作\n```bash\ngit branch -a\ngit checkout <分支名>\ngit checkout -b <新分支名>\n```\n\n### 日志\n```bash\ngit log --oneline -10\ngit log --graph --oneline\n```\n\n## 工作流程\n\n1. 先执行 `git status` 查看更改\n2. 用 `git diff` 确认具体修改\n3. `git add -A` 暂存所有更改\n4. 写明 commit 信息（简短描述）\n5. `git push` 推送到远程\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 提交前检查 `git status` 避免提交不必要的文件\n- commit 信息要有意义，方便回溯\n- 推送前确认分支正确","path":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/git-manager/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-newapi","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":25953,"output":340,"cacheRead":1280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27573,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774493769184}}
