{"type":"message","id":"e540f7b2","parentId":"29dff956","timestamp":"2026-03-26T02:58:14.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the file-organizer skill.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d28139e89d319a3522a264974f92b","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: file-organizer\ndescription: 文件整理 - 按类型分类、清理临时文件、归档管理。触发词：整理文件、清理临时、归档文件、分类\n---\n\n# File Organizer\n\n帮助整理和清理文件。\n\n## 按类型分类\n\n### 常用文件类型映射\n| 类型 | 扩展名 |\n|------|--------|\n| 文档 | .md, .txt, .pdf, .doc |\n| 代码 | .js, .ts, .py, .sh, .json |\n| 图片 | .jpg, .png, .gif, .webp |\n| 压缩 | .zip, .tar, .gz, .7z |\n| 日志 | .log, .jsonl |\n\n### 分类脚本示例\n```bash\n# 按扩展名移动文件\nfor ext in md txt json; do\n  mkdir -p \"$ext\"\n  mv *.$ext \"$ext/\" 2>/dev/null\ndone\n```\n\n## 清理临时文件\n\n### 常见临时文件\n```bash\n# 删除临时文件\nrm -f *~ .*~\nrm -f *.tmp *.temp\n\n# 清理空目录\nfind . -type d -empty -delete\n\n# 清理n天前的文件\nfind . -type f -mtime +30 -delete\n```\n\n### 特定目录清理\n```bash\n# 清理npm缓存\nrm -rf node_modules/.cache\n\n# 清理日志（保留7天）\nfind logs -name \"*.log\" -mtime +7 -delete\n```\n\n## 归档管理\n\n### 打包\n```bash\n# 打包目录\ntar -czf backup.tar.gz folder/\n\n# 按日期打包\ntar -czf \"backup_$(date +%Y%m%d).tar.gz\" folder/\n```\n\n### 解压\n```bash\ntar -xzf file.tar.gz\nunzip file.zip\n```\n\n## 安全提醒\n\n- 删除前确认文件不重要\n- 使用 `trash` 而非 `rm`（如果配置了别名）\n- 重要文件先备份再清理","path":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/file-organizer/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-newapi","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":25902,"output":500,"cacheRead":1408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27810,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774493854977}}
