{"type":"message","id":"371fd97d","parentId":"dfc82b8c","timestamp":"2026-03-26T03:57:25.193Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 当前模型配置\n\n**模型名称**: `custom-api-deepseek-com/deepseek-chat`\n- **提供商**: DeepSeek（自定义API端点）\n- **模型类型**: DeepSeek Chat\n- **配置来源**: `models.json` 中的 `api-key`\n- **成本**: 当前会话 $0.0000（1.5k输入/38输出）\n\n## 模型详情\n\n### 特点：\n1. **中文优化**：对中文支持很好，适合我们的对话\n2. **推理能力**：较强的逻辑推理和代码生成能力\n3. **上下文长度**：16k tokens（当前使用136%）\n4. **成本较低**：相比GPT-4等模型更经济\n\n### 当前会话状态：\n- **输入tokens**: 1,500\n- **输出tokens**: 38  \n- **上下文使用率**: 136%（已超过16k，自动压缩）\n- **压缩次数**: 27次（历史对话被压缩为摘要）\n\n## 其他可用模型\n\n根据我的记忆，OpenClaw支持多种模型。让我检查一下配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_n9Hw5rVeD52BiCSn5Y9VuUUW","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"模型配置 可用模型 deepseek"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":200,"output":283,"cacheRead":14080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14563,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774497435181,"responseId":"9867777f-8e21-4786-8556-c54385aa7620"}}
